{
  "texts": [
    "After subsetting the data, we computed the nearest-neighbor graph on the precomputed MultiVI 84, 87 latent space and the UMAP embedding with Scanpy.",
    "Following this, we computed 15 diffusion components 88 (scanpy.tl.diffmap) to then assign diffusion pseudotime values using Scanpy's dpt 1, 88 function with n_dcs=6.",
    "We identified the root cell as the hematopoietic stem cell with the largest fifth diffusion component.",
    "We computed the transition matrix with CellRank 2's Pseudo-timeKernel and thresholding_scheme='soft' and computed six macrostates 20.",
    "We defined the terminal states 'pDC', 'CD14 + Mono', 'Normoblast' and 'cDC2' that corresponded to the four macrostates with the largest macrostate purity."
  ]
}